- [man 4] <i>Good evening. passengers.</i>

173
00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:22.375
<i>Please be advised that flight...</i>

174
00:12:22.458 --> 00:12:25.041
- Shit.
- <i>AB304 to Kathmandu</i>

175
00:12:25.125 --> 00:12:27.291
- <i>is now boarding for departure.</i>
- Sorry. bro.

176
00:12:31.125 --> 00:12:35.750
