178
00:12:44.041 --> 00:12:45.041
<i>There he is.</i>

179
00:12:46.125 --> 00:12:48.875
- Looking spiffy.
- Yeah. I bet you say that to all the boys.

180
00:12:50.541 --> 00:12:52.291
