- Got your papers?

181
00:12:52.375 --> 00:12:53.375
Yep.

182
00:12:53.833 --> 00:12:56.291
First month. a place up north
called Fallujah.

183
00:12:57.083 --> 00:12:59.375
Isn't Northern Iraq
where all the fighting's been?

184
00:13:00.666 --> 00:13:01.750
I'm the mechanic. bro.

185
00:13:01.833 --> 00:13:04.541
The only fight I'm gonna have
is with rusty Hummer manifolds.

186
00:13:04.625 --> 00:13:07.125
Hey. you're my little brother.
I'm protective.

187
00:13:07.916 --> 00:13:11.375
- Come on. let's go. I don't wanna be late.
- [car engine starts]

188
00:13:16.791 --> 00:13:20.125
