189
00:13:27.333 --> 00:13:29.500
When I get back.
we're gonna climb Everest.

190
00:13:30.541 --> 00:13:32.541
And then we'll go into business
with our own rig.

191
00:13:35.166 --> 00:13:36.166
I love you. Mike.

192
00:13:37.791 --> 00:13:38.916
You be careful out there.

193
00:13:39.291 --> 00:13:40.291
[Gurty] Yeah.

194
00:13:41.291 --> 00:13:42.291
Oh.

195
00:13:43.208 --> 00:13:46.458
Here. they make us do this.
but. uh. I'll tear it up when I get back.

196
00:13:46.541 --> 00:13:50.166
[somber music playing]

197
00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:54.916
[PA beeps] <i>Ladies and gentlemen.</i>
<i>this is your captain speaking.</i>

198
00:13:56.166 --> 00:13:58.291
<i>We'll be touching down
in Kathmandu airport</i>

199
00:13:58.375 --> 00:14:00.583
<i>in approximately 30 minutes.</i>

200
00:14:00.666 --> 00:14:02.833
<i>If you'd like to take a look
out the port side window.</i>

201
00:14:02.916 --> 00:14:06.000
<i>you'll catch a glimpse of Everest.
the tallest mount in the world.</i>

202
00:14:06.375 --> 00:14:09.083
<i>The weather in Kathmandu
is fine with clear skies.</i>

203
00:14:09.166 --> 00:14:11.125
<i>Once again. from the flight deck
and our crew.</i>

204
00:14:11.208 --> 00:14:13.333
<i>we'd like to thank you
for flying with us today.</i>

205
00:14:13.416 --> 00:14:19.000
- <i>We hope you enjoyed it. Thank you.</i>
- [ethnic music playing]

206
00:14:24.333 --> 00:14:26.750
[indistinct chatter]

207
00:14:28.583 --> 00:14:29.708
Hello. yeah.

208
00:14:31.916 --> 00:14:32.916
Starr!

209
00:14:34.458 --> 00:14:35.333
Starr!

210
00:14:35.416 --> 00:14:37.333
[taxi drivers clamoring]

211
00:14:38.500 --> 00:14:39.833
Welcome to Kathmandu.

212
00:14:39.916 --> 00:14:40.958
- Dad.
- Let's go.

213
00:14:41.791 --> 00:14:44.291
[indistinct chatter]

214
00:14:50.250 --> 00:14:52.416
[taxi drivers clamor indistinctly]

215
00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:55.041
What is the right direction
to the city centre?

216
00:14:55.125 --> 00:14:56.958
[man 5] Too far to walk.
Much too far.

217
00:14:57.041 --> 00:14:58.441
How far?
- [man 5] Too far. Too far.

218
00:15:00.750 --> 00:15:01.958
[chuckles] Thanks. guys.

219
00:15:03.208 --> 00:15:05.125
[man 5] I'll take you to the city.
