227
00:15:39.041 --> 00:15:41.166
Some guy named Dhani Yangchen.

228
00:15:41.583 --> 00:15:42.916
[Dhani] I am Dhani.

229
00:15:46.041 --> 00:15:49.291
[indistinct chatter]

230
00:15:50.125 --> 00:15:51.333
Dhani. Got it.

231
00:15:52.791 --> 00:15:53.791
Apologies.

232
00:15:54.375 --> 00:15:55.375
Do you have the urn?

233
00:15:56.416 --> 00:15:57.416
Yep.

234
00:15:58.125 --> 00:16:01.625
- After you.
- [ethnic music playing]

235
00:16:04.458 --> 00:16:07.750
- [Dhani] First time in Kathmandu?
- First time. yeah.

236
00:16:08.625 --> 00:16:11.458
Americans either love it or hate it.

237
00:16:11.958 --> 00:16:13.208
- I love it.
- [chuckles]

238
00:16:13.750 --> 00:16:14.875
So do I.

239
00:16:15.791 --> 00:16:17.708
[Mike] Are you Hindu?

240
00:16:18.250 --> 00:16:19.250
[Dhani] No.

241
00:16:19.625 --> 00:16:20.625
Buddhist.

242
00:16:21.208 --> 00:16:23.333
- You?
- Lapsed Catholic.

243
00:16:23.416 --> 00:16:24.416
[Dhani chuckles]

244
00:16:24.625 --> 00:16:25.625
Is there hope for me?

245
00:16:27.333 --> 00:16:29.916
We're all God's children. Mr. McCann.

246
00:16:30.375 --> 00:16:31.375
Mike...

247
00:16:31.583 --> 00:16:32.583
I insist.

248
00:16:32.791 --> 00:16:34.375
Mike. Okay.

249
00:16:35.125 --> 00:16:37.083
[Mike] The Guide Service said
you were Sherpa.

250
00:16:38.583 --> 00:16:39.583
Half.

251
00:16:40.166 --> 00:16:41.458
Another half Malaysian.

252
00:16:42.083 --> 00:16:43.625
How many ascents?

253
00:16:44.583 --> 00:16:46.041
- Mount Everest?
- Yeah.

254
00:16:46.500 --> 00:16:47.500
Ten.

255
00:16:47.791 --> 00:16:49.416
Ten. Wow.

256
00:16:50.250 --> 00:16:51.250
Impressive.

257
00:16:52.791 --> 00:16:53.916
